title: Cisco ASA: Connections
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/cisco
license: GPLv3
distribution: check_mk
description:

 The Cisco ASA does have active connections for adsl/sdsl, mangement, etc. This
 check monitors the expected and actual state of these connections. Also
 it checks for the IP Address of a connection. The state will be {CRIT}
 if a connection is down or it has no IP Address assigned.


item:
  One item for each connection is generated.

discovery:
  One service is created for each connection.
